---
// About section component rediseñado
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="about-section">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="section-header" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div class="section-badge">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
        Personal Trainer Certificado
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        Conoce a <span class="highlight">JeanFit</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-description">
        Tu entrenador personal dedicado a transformar vidas a través del fitness y la nutrición.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Content Card -->
      <div class="content-card" data-aos="fade-right">
        <div class="experience-features">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon experience-icon">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Experiencia Profesional</h3>
              <p>Más de 10 años ayudando a personas a alcanzar sus objetivos fitness con metodologías innovadoras y resultados comprobados.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon education-icon">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Educación Continua</h3>
              <p>Constantemente actualizando conocimientos en las últimas tendencias de fitness, nutrición y metodologías de entrenamiento.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-icon personalized-icon">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-content">
              <h3>Enfoque Personalizado</h3>
              <p>Cada plan está diseñado específicamente para tus objetivos, nivel actual y estilo de vida, creando una experiencia única.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Specialties Card -->
        <div class="specialties-card">
          <h3>Especialidades y Metodologías</h3>
          <div class="specialties-grid">
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <div class="specialty-icon strength-icon">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="specialty-content">
                <span class="specialty-title">Fuerza & Resistencia</span>
                <span class="specialty-desc">Programas de alta intensidad</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <div class="specialty-icon transformation-icon">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="specialty-content">
                <span class="specialty-title">Transformación Corporal</span>
                <span class="specialty-desc">Recomposición efectiva</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <div class="specialty-icon nutrition-icon">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="specialty-content">
                <span class="specialty-title">Nutrición Estratégica</span>
                <span class="specialty-desc">Planes alimentarios personalizados</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <div class="specialty-icon mindset-icon">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="specialty-content">
                <span class="specialty-title">Mentalidad Ganadora</span>
                <span class="specialty-desc">Coaching motivacional</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="#contacto" class="primary-btn">
            <span>Comenzar Mi Transformación</span>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/jeanfit_personal_trainer" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="secondary-btn">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
            </svg>
            Seguir en Instagram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image and Stats Card -->
      <div class="image-stats-card" data-aos="fade-left">
        <!-- Profile Image -->
        <div class="profile-section">
          <div class="profile-image">
            <img src="/contacto_jeanfit.jpg" alt="JeanFit Personal Trainer" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="image-overlay">
              <div class="availability-badge">
                <span>¡Disponible!</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="profile-info">
            <h3>JeanFit</h3>
            <p>Personal Trainer & Coach de Nutrición</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats Grid -->
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <div class="stat-number">500+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Clientes Satisfechos</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <div class="stat-number">10+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Años de Experiencia</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <div class="stat-number">95%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tasa de Éxito</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
            <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Soporte Disponible</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional Info Cards -->
        <div class="info-cards">
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="info-content">
              <span class="info-title">Horarios Flexibles</span>
              <span class="info-desc">Adaptados a tu rutina</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="info-content">
              <span class="info-title">Seguimiento Continuo</span>
              <span class="info-desc">Monitoreo de progreso</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-icon">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="info-content">
              <span class="info-title">Resultados Medibles</span>
              <span class="info-desc">Progreso cuantificable</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Service Badge -->
        <div class="service-badge">
          <span>Online & Presencial</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Statement -->
    <div class="mission-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <div class="mission-content">
        <h3>Mi Misión</h3>
        <blockquote>
          "Transformar vidas a través del fitness y la nutrición, proporcionando herramientas, conocimiento y motivación para que cada persona alcance su mejor versión. Creo firmemente que el cambio es posible con la guía correcta y la dedicación constante."
        </blockquote>
        <div class="mission-author">
          <span>- JeanFit</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
      #f8fafc 0%, 
      #f1f5f9 25%, 
      #e2e8f0 50%, 
      #f1f5f9 75%, 
      #f8fafc 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container-custom {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  /* Section Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.1) 0%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 50px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-title .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD600 0%, #ed1c24 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* About Grid */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .content-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .content-card:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -4px, 0);
  }

  /* Experience Features */
  .experience-features {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: white;
  }

  .experience-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
  }

  .education-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
  }

  .personalized-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #dc2626 100%);
  }

  .feature-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .feature-content p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Specialties */
  .specialties-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.05) 0%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .specialties-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .specialties-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .specialty-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .specialty-item:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
  }

  .specialty-icon {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .strength-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #dc2626 100%);
  }

  .transformation-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
  }

  .nutrition-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
  }

  .mindset-icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
  }

  .specialty-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .specialty-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .specialty-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  /* CTA Buttons */
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .primary-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #dc2626 100%);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s ease-out;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
  }

  .primary-btn:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #ef4444 100%);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
  }

  .secondary-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .secondary-btn:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Image and Stats Card */
  .image-stats-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    position: relative;
    transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0);
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .image-stats-card:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -4px, 0);
  }

  .profile-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .profile-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .profile-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .availability-badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
  }

  .profile-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .profile-info p {
    color: #4a5568;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* Stats Grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.05) 0%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD600 0%, #ed1c24 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Additional Info Cards */
  .info-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .info-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.05) 0%, rgba(237, 28, 36, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.15);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.15s ease-out;
  }

  .info-card:hover {
    transform: translate3d(0, -2px, 0);
    border-color: rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 214, 0, 0.1);
  }

